                     <interp inst="t18450616-1363-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>stealing 3 1/2 pairs of leather fronts for boots, value 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18450616-name-670" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450616-name-670" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450616-name-670" type="surname" value="BURLINGSON"></interp>
