                        <interp inst="t18450616-name-673" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY FOWLER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 111.) I went with the prosecutor to search Crawley's premises—what he has stated is the truth.</p>
               <p>(Taylor received a good character.)</p>
